{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The guards were Germans, which were direct under the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one who ran the whole deal was a big Gestapo officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we-- the first day, they let us stay in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The camp was run like the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a police chief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a chief of the camp, which were Jews on the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But outside was the-- the-- the Nazi guards, the-- not Nazi guards, the Nazi commanders and his-- his cronies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The camp was run by them and this so-called Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them were real bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They all had bull whips and would hit you and would take advantage of you in any way they could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, everybody was hit, more or less.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- but to-- to show us where we really were, I give you the drill, which is really gruesome.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- the first Sunday, we were told-- Sunday, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First Sunday, we were told to dress up in-- in good clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were marched into the stadium of Posen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The stadium and the-- and the dressing rooms and underneath the stands was also a camp, which were working at the same-- well, I'll come back to what we were doing there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to show us in which situation we were, we were marched into the stadium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The infield of the stadium, on a-- on the track, on one side in-- in front of the-- of the grandstands, there were five gallows with four noose each, with, like, a cross over.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on each end was a-- was a-- a noose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So with other words, there was room to hang 20 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
